General stuff
-------------
* Any combination of local human, remote human and AI players
* Customizable / scriptable game types

Game types
----------
* Classic
	- Last man standing scores
	- New map after kill
	- Best out of three (not counting draws)
* Death match
	- Immediate respawn
	- No new map after death
	- Time / kill limit
* Tag
	- One player starts with Punch
	- No other power-ups
	- Punch rotates

